summary: If the writing team post-OMD was so intent on making Peter a manchild who lives with his Aunt (which he hasn’t been since that...
body: If the writing team post-OMD was so intent on making Peter a manchild who lives with his Aunt (which he hasn’t been since that time all of his and his wife’s [oh, right] money was held up on an expensive apartment because of Jonathan Caesar, and fun fact! He almost spent the night on the street because he didn’t want to go back to living with his Aunt!), the least they could’ve done was keep May in character and have her be an enabler.
